<body_title>
How to use MKDOCS

<description>
mkdocs (make docs) - utility written in pure python designed to generate different docs format (like HTML) from single .doc formatted files

<usage>
mkdocs dir docsdir htmldir

<examples end=</examples>>

<example 1 end="@example 1 end">
mkdocs file file.doc page.html
@example 1 end